{"section": "Exercise 3.21.3: Solving linear homogeneous recurrence relations.", "qid": 4, "instructions": "<div class=\"setup\">\n <p>\n  Solve each of the following recurrence equations with the given initial values.\n </p>\n</div>\n", "input_type": null, "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <span class=\"part\">\n  (e)\n </span>\n <div class=\"text\">\n  <p>\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    b\n    <sub>\n     n\n    </sub>\n    = 3b\n    <sub>\n     n\u22121\n    </sub>\n    + 4b\n    <sub>\n     n\u22122\n    </sub>\n    - 12b\n    <sub>\n     n\u22123\n    </sub>\n   </span>\n   .\n\u00a0\u00a0\nInitial values:\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    b\n    <sub>\n     0\n    </sub>\n    = 4\n   </span>\n   ,\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    b\n    <sub>\n     1\n    </sub>\n    = \u22125\n   </span>\n   ,\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    b\n    <sub>\n     2\n    </sub>\n    = 11\n   </span>\n   .\n  </p>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "choices": [], "correct_choice_index": null, "answer": "3(-2)n +2n+1  - 3n", "explanation": null, "images": {"instructions": "3.21.3-exercise-instructions_div.png", "question": "3.21.3.4-exercise-question.png", "choices": []}}